Loved the movie!! When will amazon have the soundtrack of this movie for sale?
Love this movie, a true addiction.
This is a touching film. We all need to put things in perspective when it comes to relationships and overcome all the imposed criteria, be it family member's judgement, education, society rules, etc.

A woman finds herself falling in love with a man with whom she is initially doesn't find physically appealingly.  A heartwarming old fashion movie that serves as a good reminder of what's really important in relationships of the heart.  It's so easy to pass judgement on others who don't meet our criteria for "normal", especially in today's society.  The characters in this movie are charming and entertaining.
Could not be played on the dvd player/ blue ray, needed an external hard drive. The dubbing did not correspond to the action.
I love this movie!!! but, the dvd you sent me was not good. I returned it!
